  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Marketing Outreach Rep",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Marketing Outreach Rep</strong></h2><p>💬 <strong>Like meeting new people, learning on the go, and doing work that’s not stuck behind a desk?</strong><br />At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, you’ll be part of real-life campaigns where you interact with the public, represent brands, and build confidence through hands-on experience. This role is active, social, and designed for learning by doing.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><p>👋 Chat with members of the public through friendly, face-to-face interactions<br />🎤 Support brand presentations at events, roadshows, and outreach activities<br />💬 Pick up communication and people skills through real-world experience<br />🤝 Work with a supportive team to run campaigns smoothly</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></h3><p>🎓 Training provided in sales, communication, and outreach<br />📈 Clear, performance-based growth opportunities<br />🌍 Exposure to different campaigns and working locations<br />🤝 Mentorship, guidance, and a collaborative team culture</p><h3><strong>This Role Is Great For You If You</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Enjoy talking to people or want to build confidence</p></li><li><p>Are open to learning and improving through feedback</p></li><li><p>Like being active and working in fast-paced environments</p></li><li><p>Prefer hands-on experience over desk-based work</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Who May Enjoy This Role</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Individuals exploring marketing or customer engagement</p></li><li><p>Those looking to gain practical, real-world experience</p></li><li><p>People who enjoy teamwork and meeting new people</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Interested in building real-world skills while working with people and brands?<br />📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
